result.name: Genebank 2.0: Resistance gene capture in winter wheat diversity panels
result.description: RenSeq was conducted  for a panel of 917  winter wheat genotypes including European elite varieties, PGR material from the IPK collection  and the reference genotype Chinese Spring. Triticeae RenSeq Baits V3 (Tv3) probe set comprising 200,000 oligonucleotide baits were used for sequencing.
result.center: IPK Gatersleben - Leibniz Institute of Plant Genetics and Crop Plant Research
